{"tid":1672623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTai退役軍人軍師[sosad]笑到我胃出血[sosad]","createTime":"2019-10-24T08:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T09:54:06.000Z","uid":214972,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"73eceef633b2d8ecb454721c928d9164b62d2415","tid":1672623,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"香港人，係時候接受長期抗爭需要大台嘅現實了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n裡面話<br />\n<blockquote>好多人誤以為美國佬通過人權法案之後就會一天都光，<span style=\"color: red;\">作為一個退役軍人</span>，我想話畀大家知，美國佬依啲議案好多時都係形式主義，短期內唔會實際拎嚟用，就好似上戰場之前要生產武器咁，但生產完把武器未必會拎嚟用，只係以防萬一。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起一起底原來係俾家姐恰嘅白咭佬ff做傭兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNArVe5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNArVe5.png&h=55062667&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm98o8r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm98o8r.png&h=c8b52e19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1xaCts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1xaCts.png&h=b3b36fd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a1c17acb800601ff1faa1d972c23b7a4a5e3a57","tid":1672623,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"［各國旗手全面進場］今晚人權集會喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ba72f17ddc3724a5419ae7bfb4fc8d9a7f75224","tid":1672623,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030b6f6217eb978b4c